Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了她？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是执行官杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你心痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有点悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你有照我的吩咐吃药啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看看你的色相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很清澈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到只是吃了一点据说不管用的药
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然就能觉得这么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有适合自己的固有处方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不考虑这一点 只是一味下猛药
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与施暴无异
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要帮我改善色相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想要你本人意愿的首肯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先知系统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能审判你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去后门那边调查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.14,system,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪系数 26+
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.22,system,NTP,0,0,0,,刑事科在籍监视官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:08.44,system,NTP,0,0,0,,警告 执行官的反叛行为将被记录并上报总部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够清澈的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事
